Liverpool fans rejoice... you may not be getting Christian Pulisic but how about Real Madrid's Marco Asensio?<br />
<br />
Spanish journalist Eduardo Inda told Spanish publication OK Diario: &quot;This year, an offer of &euro;180m came to Real Madrid from Liverpool for Asensio. The club said no because Cristiano [Ronaldo] left, but [Jurgen] Klopp is in love with the player and will go for him next summer.&quot;
